sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Ray Client
    participant Route as Ray Client Route/Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ passthrough
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Service<br/>10001/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant RayWorker as Ray Workers<br/>gRPC mTLS

    Note over Client,RayWorker: Flow 3: Ray Client Connection with mTLS

    Client->>Route: Connect<br/>Auth: Client Certificate
    Route->>RayHead: Forward gRPC<br/>mTLS Client Certificate
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Distribute work<br/>mTLS
    RayWorker-->>RayHead: Results
    RayHead-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>Client: gRPC Response
